<div class="mw-parser-output"><h1>Brain</h1>
<p>Brain is a character attribute and represents a combination of Intelligence, Wisdom, Awareness,
PSI and Perception.
</p><p>Brain Determines:
</p>
<ul><li>A factor in deciding if you hit another character with a magic attack.</li>
<li>A factor in deciding if you defend against a magic attack.</li>
<li>A factor in discovering theft, sneaking and hidden.</li></ul>
